# Plan 12-04: API Routes + UI Enrichment Hooks

<objective>
Wire the analysis service into the API router with feature-gated endpoints, and build frontend enrichment components that render AI analysis data when available and degrade gracefully to empty states when not.

All UI blocks are behind feature flag checks — both backend (404 when disabled) and frontend (hidden when disabled).
</objective>

<threat_model>
**Attack Surface:** New API endpoints exposing analysis data, frontend rendering of AI-generated content.
**Threats:**
- Unauthorized access to analysis endpoints (MEDIUM) — must require authentication + organization scope
- XSS via AI-generated teaching card content (HIGH) — must sanitize before rendering
- Information disclosure through analysis data (LOW) — tenant isolation enforced at service layer
**Mitigations:**
- All routes require JWT auth middleware (inherited from API middleware stack)
- Frontend uses DOMPurify (already in project) to sanitize AI-generated HTML
- Analysis service queries always filter by organization_id from JWT claims
- Feature flag check returns 404 (not 403) per D-08, hiding endpoint existence
**Block on:** HIGH — XSS through AI-generated content
</threat_model>

